## 概述

Bitget V2 Mix API 是 USDT/USDC/COIN 保证金永续合约接口。特点：需要 PASSPHRASE 认证、签名用 Base64 编码。

| 项目 | 值 |
|------|-----|
| REST Base URL | `https://api.bitget.com` |
| WS Public | `wss://ws.bitget.com/v2/ws/public` |
| WS Private | `wss://ws.bitget.com/v2/ws/private` |
| WS Demo Public | `wss://wspap.bitget.com/v2/ws/public` |
| WS Demo Private | `wss://wspap.bitget.com/v2/ws/private` |
| 认证方式 | HMAC-SHA256 + **Base64** + PASSPHRASE |
| Python SDK | `pip install python-bitget` |

