## Python SDK

```bash
pip install python-bitget
```

```python
from pybitget import Client

client = Client(api_key, api_secret, passphrase=passphrase)

# 查账户
result = client.mix_get_accounts(productType='USDT-FUTURES')

# WebSocket
from pybitget.stream import BitgetWsClient, SubscribeReq

ws = BitgetWsClient(
    api_key=api_key, api_secret=api_secret,
    passphrase=passphrase, verbose=True
).build()

channels = [SubscribeReq("USDT-FUTURES", "ticker", "BTCUSDT")]
ws.subscribe(channels, callback)
```

也可用 `ccxt`：`pip install ccxt`

